      "rationale": "RH index bias computed as (CFD-Exp)/Exp for each of 5 operating points. Maximum bias 8.3% at 3 L/min/4000 rpm; minimum bias 1.2% at 5 L/min/3000 rpm. All within ±15% acceptance band. Precision (1-sigma repeatability) estimated from triplicate experimental runs: 4.1% average."
