      "rationale": "Validation experiments span 3–6 L/min and 3000–4500 rpm, encompassing the COU operating envelope of 4–5 L/min and 3200–4200 rpm. FDA generic pump geometry used in both validation and COU simulations. Similarity index computed per ASME V&V 40 Appendix C: 0.87 (threshold 0.70). Validation activities judged adequately relevant to COU."
