      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis model selection justified with literature support and sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating machinery hemolysis applications (Giersiepen et al., Zhang et al.). Power-law hemolysis model (Heuser-Opitz) applied. Sensitivity analysis comparing SST k-omega vs. realizable k-epsilon shows < 6% difference in RH index across operating envelope. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±10% and incorporated into acceptance band definition."
    },
    {
